{"tid":2075938,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"11哥：國安法或將醫管局及競委會、監警會等法定組織納入「公職人員」定義 日後就任時需要宣誓","createTime":"2020-06-23T07:14:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T08:05:15.000Z","uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cbd8873814d37efd7bc9ed5fdc8a014979017cf4","tid":2075938,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T07:14:20.000Z","msg":"早前公佈《港版國安法》草案說明指出，香港居民在參選或就任公職時應當依法簽署文件確認或者宣誓擁護《基本法》及效忠特區。行政會議成員、資深大律師湯家驊接受《星島》訪問時指，公職人員的定義廣闊，除公務員外，醫管局及競委會、監警會等法定委員會的人員也可能屬公職人員，惟詳情要視乎「港版國安法」實際條文才可界定。《蘋果》正向醫管局查詢是否知悉事件。<br />\n<br />\n詳情：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200623/YBP6H74LVVWDZZFXTSNXCQU7WQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200623%2FYBP6H74LVVWDZZFXTSNXCQU7WQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=%2FOWxXeQsMLcQIgbDBmmt7vroWj9UcGxh4mdojqPZn1M%3D&h=d1647001\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200623%2FYBP6H74LVVWDZZFXTSNXCQU7WQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=4e835843\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200623/YBP6H74LVVWDZZFXTSNXCQU7WQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"5d6e609a6cef6957117105b1135e4a91e26ac694","tid":2075938,"uid":19725,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T07:15:48.000Z","msg":"有公務員福利？哈"},{"pid":"51035e1463ec01f1e944530a3ae2ad2b19f73de4","tid":2075938,"uid":58031,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T07:17:58.000Z","msg":"冇公務員福利，有公務員責任<br />\n以支那血性，九成係咁"},{"pid":"e1ccce5aa6164b6e20f91ddd14d8554cd3eb4645","tid":20759